casebody.data:
David A. ZUBIK, et al., petitioners,
v.
Sylvia BURWELL, Secretary of Health and Human Services, et al. No. 14-1418. Supreme Court of the United States Nov. 6, 2015.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit granted limited to Question 1 presented by the petition. The case is consolidated.
